message.body: I just remembered I don't have to come in early this week. Guess I'll take my time making breakfast and relaxing lol
You up yet? Should probably try to readjust your sleep pattern although that should've stayed last week
Started*
Well I'm up, let's see if I stay up...
￼Breakfast is served!
It sure is. What time are you planning to go in?
Within the hour
It's cold outside!!!
Triple layer!
Sorry if I sounded seemed unsupportive. That's some of the tendencies coming from my mother I'm slowly phasing out.
Howdy. How are things?
Good. Had a birthday lunch with my family, and now I'm back home settling down :) How was work?
Still here. I have late shift this week. Getting out at 7. Bambu later?
You beat me to it. I was going to send you the picture.
Ah bugger
Yea, my mom, my sister, and I went to get some.
Feel like watching House of Cards?
Of course. Would I be out of line if I asked you to pick me up from south Philly lol
I'm going to be home for a while longer. Was thinking about later tonight. What time do you get out?
I'm out at 7 then I'm gonna pick up something from my friend. If you wanna stay home until later that's fine
Well I have a phone date with Uyen, but I don't know the time so I'll be waiting for her call.
Alright. You do you then. No biggie. Lemme knew when you're fine with Uyen :)
Hey, would you mind if we watch another night? It got late and I think I'm going to stay in for the rest of the night.
That's fine. I figured as much once it got past 8 heh.
Yea, I talked to Uyen until nine something. Great. Frank Underwood will have to wait hahah.
That's ok. I have Phoebe and Ross entertaining me
Friends. Solid choice. I think you're missing a few names there.
I meant to say Chandler not Ross. They're my favorite of the bunch.
Omgah Helen hunt!
How was your phone date?
It was good, really nice to catch up with each other.
I conked out early. Feels nice not struggling to sleep heh
